Title: An Act Changing the Name of Barangay Diongan in the Municipality of Siayan, Province of Zamboanga Del Norte, to Barangay Datu Tangkilan Andus
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 679
An Act Changing the Name of Barangay Diongan in the Municipality of Siayan, Province of Zamboanga Del Norte, to Barangay Datu Tangkilan Andus
Section 1. The name of Barangay Diongan in the Municipality of Siayan, Province of Zamboanga del Norte, is changed to Barangay Datu Tangkilan Andus.1awp++i1
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: March 7, 1984
